data.description: 4-bed property in Johnson Ranch! Discover a captivating interior showcasing dining & living areas with bountiful natural light, designer palette throughout, vaulted ceilings, plantation shutters, neutral tile floor, & soft carpet in all the right places. The fabulous kitchen , speckled granite counters, a pantry, SS appliances, modern recessed lighting, stylish tile backsplash, & an island with a breakfast bar. Double doors open to the main suite offering a private bath with dual sinks, a walk-in closet, & outdoor access. You'll love hosting fun gatherings in the amazing backyard featuring a full-length covered patio, a crystal clear swimming pool, in-ground trampoline, & mesmerizing mountain views! Don't miss out!
